name: symbols_get_profile
description:
This is a sub-function API for tool cnbc.
Tool description: This API helps to query for business news and live market data to create a financial site such as cnbc.com
API description: Fetch summary information for a stock quote, index, exchange, etc., given an issue ID.

issueid.description: The value of the issueId field obtained from previous endpoints such as .../auto-complete or .../symbols/translate.
